====Transitive verb====
'''to fan''' ([[fans]], [[fanned]], [[fanning]])
# to [[blow]] air on (something) by means of a fan (hand-held, mechanical or electrical) or otherwise
#:''We enjoyed standing at the edge of the cliff, being '''fanned''' by the wind.''

