===Etymology 2===
Shortened from ''[[fanatic]]''

====Noun====
'''fan''' (''plural:'' [[fans]])
#An [[admirer]] or [[aficionado]], especially of a [[sport]] or [[performer]]; someone who is [[fond]] of something or someone; an [[admirer]]
#:''I am a big '''fan''' of libraries.''

